 Nigerian Veteran Dancer, Kafayat Shafau aka Kaffy is not impressed with the new dance Naira Marley introduced last week when he dropped “Soapy”, his first single since being released from EFCC custody. Kaffy revealed on instagram that she is less impressed about the dance, which she tagged “Immoral”. She wrote; This is a No . #myopinion As dancers we should also speak for what is right we shouldn’t encourage this for the sake of trend. Esp when it’s not even censored away from kids ,as an adult sef it’s offensive. #rubbish  The post Dance Queen, Kaffy Rubbishes Naira Marley’s “Immoral” Soapy Dance appeared first on . Source: 36Ng